{"tid":548904,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"真漢子請進","createTime":"2018-02-03T06:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T07:44:58.000Z","uid":7248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e833f2845d92fa89ec8ebf036a178ba70afb5dc2","tid":548904,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀，去強姦。人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲。愛她就去搞她，喜歡就去強姦。表白有什麼用還是會被拒絕。追不到就下藥，翻臉就發裸照。大不了蹲監獄，你連監獄都不敢蹲還好意思說愛她。出來之後找到她繼續強姦，強姦到讓她開始懷疑自己的人生，讓她覺得她人生的意義就是被你強姦。"},{"pid":"2aff81ebc673a62932dac21a74479f22dfc5fbb2","tid":548904,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:43:38.000Z","msg":"你幾時可以俾我強姦"},{"pid":"2342815674087ca1e2493b860ee16a768d1de52f","tid":548904,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aff81ebc673a62932dac21a74479f22dfc5fbb2","tid":548904,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T06:43:38.000Z","msg":"你幾時可以俾我強姦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T07:31:11.000Z","msg":"Never"},{"pid":"102cafccbb629e52ddb41cd8cd3516df7860556f","tid":548904,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T07:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你幾時可以俾我強姦</blockquote>Never</blockquote><br />\n咁我落藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123ef622347587cfad45e41742441c2d7de7ac38","tid":548904,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"102cafccbb629e52ddb41cd8cd3516df7860556f","tid":548904,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T07:38:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你幾時可以俾我強姦</blockquote>Never</blockquote><br />\n咁我落藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"玩屁肌犯法"}]}